
## Right Rotate an array by k-places
- **🔗 Problem Link:** [Right Rotate an array by k-places](https://leetcode.com/problems/rotate-array/)
- **📌 Date:** 2025-02-28 07:40
- **💡 Approach:** 1. Reverse the last 'k' elements   &  2. Reverse the remaining elements from start (0 -> n-k-1)  &  3. Reverse the whole array.
- **❌ Mistakes & Improvements:** 


### Solution:
```java
class Solution {
    public static void reverse(int[] a, int start, int end){
        while(start < end){
            int t = a[start];
            a[start] = a[end];
            a[end] = t;
            start++;
            end--;
        }
    }

    public void rotate(int[] nums, int k) {
        int n = nums.length;
        k = k % n;

        reverse(nums, 0, n-k-1);
        reverse(nums, n-k, n-1);
        reverse(nums, 0, n-1);
    }
} ```
